item.description: When we came to this earth at birth, we came with guidance. We have the ability to open up our energy field and feel their presence. We can tap into that energy and find answers to questions and remove fear and doubts. This program warms your soul and allows you to have more clear communication with your personal Masters and Guides. Join us for a 2-hour program that will leave you wanting more. Fee: $15 in advance, $25 at the door.
